sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户程序
    participant CUDART as libcudart<br/>1.4 MB
    participant CUDA as libcuda.so<br/>87 MB
    participant KERNEL as nvidia.ko<br/>~101 MB
    participant GPU as GPU 硬件

    User->>CUDART: cudaMalloc(4MB)
    CUDART->>CUDA: cuMemAlloc_v2()
    CUDA->>KERNEL: open("/dev/nvidia0")
    CUDA->>KERNEL: ioctl(0x2a, ...)
    KERNEL-->>CUDA: GPU 显存地址
    CUDA-->>CUDART: CUDA_SUCCESS
    CUDART-->>User: d_a

    User->>CUDART: cudaMemcpy(H2D, 4MB)
    CUDART->>CUDA: cuMemcpyHtoD_v2()
    CUDA->>KERNEL: ioctl(0x4e, DMA desc)
    KERNEL-->>GPU: PCIe DMA 传输
    GPU-->>KERNEL: DMA 完成
    KERNEL-->>CUDA: 完成
    CUDA-->>CUDART: CUDA_SUCCESS
    CUDART-->>User: OK

    User->>CUDART: cudaLaunchKernel()
    CUDART->>CUDA: cuLaunchKernel()
    CUDA->>KERNEL: 构建 command buffer
    CUDA->>KERNEL: ioctl(0x4e, cmd)
    KERNEL-->>GPU: 推送到命令队列
    GPU->>GPU: Warp Scheduler
    GPU->>GPU: SASS 执行
    Note over GPU: LDG.E / FADD / STG.E / EXIT

    User->>CUDART: cudaDeviceSynchronize()
    CUDART->>CUDA: cuCtxSynchronize_v2()
    CUDA->>KERNEL: ioctl(0x2b, fence)
    KERNEL-->>GPU: 查询 fence 寄存器
    GPU-->>KERNEL: 完成
    KERNEL->>KERNEL: eventfd → futex
    KERNEL-->>CUDA: GPU 完成
    CUDA-->>CUDART: CUDA_SUCCESS
    CUDART-->>User: 同步完成
